flowchart LR
    PO["📄 .po file"]

    PO --> UP["1️⃣ npm run upload-prompt -- &lt;po-file&gt;"]
    UP --> UP1["Prompt template stored in Langfuse"]

    PO --> UD["2️⃣ npm run upload-dataset -- &lt;po-file&gt; [--limit N]"]
    UD --> UD1["Human translations uploaded as baseline dataset in Langfuse"]

    PO --> EV["3️⃣ npm run eval -- &lt;po-file&gt; --model &lt;model&gt; [--limit N]"]
    EV --> EV1["AI translates each entry via OpenAI model"]
    EV1 --> EV2["Scored against human baseline — BLEU · chrF · LLM judge"]
    EV2 --> EV3["Results logged to Langfuse"]
